<bibRefCitation id="C52466A8BF4AFF8A1993FC909D6AFCB1" author="Nilsson, A. N." box="[1217,1372,788,815]" pageId="23" pageNumber="274" pagination="35 - 96" refId="ref33005" refString="Nilsson, A. N. (1995) Noteridae and Dytiscidae: Annotated check list of the Noteridae and Dytiscidae of China (Coleoptera). In: Jach, M. A. &amp; Ji, L. (Eds.), Water beetles of China. Vol. I. Zoologisch-Botanische Gesellschaft in Osterreich and Wiener Coleopterologenverein, Wien, pp. 35 - 96." type="book chapter" year="1995">Nilsson 1995</bibRefCitation>
